Hello everyone,

Today, I have a sad announcement to makeüò¢
After more than 6 years of Spotify bot, that unfortunate time has come.
Yes, that's right, the bot will be shut down.

Unfortunately, due to personal reasons, I no longer have the time or resources to keep the bot up and operational.

The bot will be taken offline, effective February 8th.

Thank you for all these years of support, thank you to every one who believed in this project, thank you to every last user of this bot, and a special thank you goes to all the people that donated to help keep the bot alive for all this time‚ù§Ô∏è

DevNull, out.
